{
  "page": "Ghiscari Dawn",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><i><b>Ghiscari Dawn</b></i> is a slaver galley out of <a href=\"/index.php/New_Ghis\" title=\"New Ghis\">New Ghis</a>. It is renamed <i><b>Red God's Wroth</b></i> after its capture by the <a href=\"/index.php/Ironborn\" title=\"Ironborn\">ironborn</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recent_Events\">Recent Events</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ghiscari_Dawn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Recent Events\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"A_Dance_with_Dragons\"><i>A Dance with Dragons</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ghiscari_Dawn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: A Dance with Dragons\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p><i>Ghiscari Dawn</i> trades at <a href=\"/index.php/Meereen\" title=\"Meereen\">Meereen</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Yunkai\" title=\"Yunkai\">Yunkai</a>. While returning to <a href=\"/index.php/New_Ghis\" title=\"New Ghis\">New Ghis</a>, it encounters the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Fleet\" title=\"Iron Fleet\">Iron Fleet</a> in the strait between the <a href=\"/index.php/Isle_of_Cedars\" title=\"Isle of Cedars\">Isle of Cedars</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Astapor\" title=\"Astapor\">Astapor</a>'s hinterland. <i>Ghiscari Dawn</i> is captured by <i><a href=\"/index.php/Lamentation_(ship)\" title=\"Lamentation (ship)\">Lamentation</a></i> near <a href=\"/index.php/Ghozai\" title=\"Ghozai\">Ghozai</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Victarion_Greyjoy\" title=\"Victarion Greyjoy\">Victarion Greyjoy</a> has its captain drowned as a sacrifice to the <a href=\"/index.php/Drowned_God\" title=\"Drowned God\">Drowned God</a>. The ship is renamed <i>Red God's Wroth</i> by Victarion in honor of <a href=\"/index.php/R%27hllor\" title=\"R&#39;hllor\">R'hllor</a>, the god worshiped by the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_priest\" title=\"Red priest\">red priest</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Moqorro\" title=\"Moqorro\">Moqorro</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Radwd63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Radwd63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Ghiscari_Dawn&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Radwd63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Radwd63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_63\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 63\">Chapter 63</a>, Victarion I.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403093026\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.022 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.043 secon